name: new stock
query:
SELECT 
    bin.item_code,
    SUM(bin.projected_qty) AS total_projected_qty,
    SUM(bin.reserved_qty) AS total_reserved_qty,
    SUM(bin.reserved_qty_for_production) AS total_reserved_qty_for_production,
    SUM(bin.reserved_qty_for_sub_contract) AS total_reserved_qty_for_sub_contract,
    SUM(bin.actual_qty) AS total_actual_qty,
    AVG(bin.valuation_rate) AS average_valuation_rate
FROM 
    `tabBin` AS bin
WHERE 
    (bin.projected_qty != 0 OR 
    bin.reserved_qty != 0 OR 
    bin.reserved_qty_for_production != 0 OR 
    bin.reserved_qty_for_sub_contract != 0 OR 
    bin.actual_qty != 0)
GROUP BY 
    bin.item_code
ORDER BY 
    total_actual_qty DESC;
